of the normal channel


56
00:02:56,376 --> 00:02:58,712 line:-1
to their organization
in Apple School Manager


57
00:02:58.712 --> 00:03:02.049 line:-1 position:50%
or Apple Business Manager.


58
00:03:02,049 --> 00:03:05,285 line:-1
In Setup Assistant on a Mac,


59
00:03:05.285 --> 00:03:07.487 line:-1 position:50%
